name: CLIP's Ahoy
description:
This batch of 12 CLIP's Ahoy cookies is the artist's first NFT. He's wagering that the way to your heart is through your stomach. Apparently he's as shit at anatomy as he is at naming things.

But what can I say.. That's one classy-looking cookie. With such an iconic name in the form of a bad machine learning in-joke, how could one resist?
